data.description: Enjoy sitting on the deck/patio areas in your parklike yard with flowering trees everywhere! Nice sized rambler on 8 acres with room for your equine friends! New flooring, paint, countertops, roof, pressure tank/pump, frost free spigots, wired for generator and more. Close to Olympia, 5 min to I-5 shopping, restaurants, casino and still has a hobby farm feel. Heated garage has a car lift, insulated & GUN ROOM. Two stall barn with lean-to has indoor/outdoor kennels. Fenced & cross fenced with permanent  horse shelters and a large yard with beautiful evergreens, circular drive w/ a lighted iron gate entry. The 1.3 acre parcel adjoining has a large equipment shed and power installed and can be purchased separately.
